Text: Thank you! The other versions of this are either way bigger than they need to be, or, in one case, the bitrate is too low for 1080p (see anoXmous/Zen-Bud.) Perfect balance between file size and quality on this one though. Great job!

I agree. I was about to download anoXmous' until I saw the bitrates. Substandard. This is the ONLY decent low file size/high quality encode of Snatch in 1080p. Judging from the number of seeds though, it's clear that most people are clueless when it comes to bitrates and good encoding. Thank you Jalucian.
